sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub Repo
    participant CP as AWS CodePipeline
    participant CB as AWS CodeBuild
    participant CD as AWS CodeDeploy
    participant ASG as Backend ASG (EC2 instances)
    participant ALB as Application Load Balancer

    Dev->>GH: git push (Commit)
    GH-->>CP: Webhook / CodeStar Connection trigger
    CP->>CB: Start Build stage
    CB->>CB: npm ci, npm test, package appspec.yml + scripts + backend/ into zip
    CB-->>CP: Build artifact (zip) stored in S3
    CP->>CD: Start Deploy stage
    CD->>ASG: ApplicationStop
    CD->>ASG: BeforeInstall
    CD->>ASG: AfterInstall (npm ci --omit=dev, write systemd unit)
    CD->>ASG: ApplicationStart (systemctl start backend)
    CD->>ASG: ValidateService (curl localhost/health)
    ASG-->>ALB: Register as healthy target
    ALB-->>Dev: Serves updated version at ALB DNS

    Note over Dev,ALB: Commit -> Build -> Deploy -> Auto Scaling Group
